title: Guardian's Crusade (Knight and Baby) PS1
description:
Guardian's Crusade...

I found this in a drawer somewhere and some years later got bored and booted it up in my PS3. I was pretty blown away by it, so I ripped it, play it in my emulator, and checked to make sure that it was available on torrent. Upon seeing that an obscure, hidden gem like this cute but very fun JRPG had no uploads, I changed that.

This is a .zip file, so do make sure to unzip it. BIN and CUE files are included so you can burn it to a disc or load it in an emulator
